{"tid":1049962,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"亞當夏娃是中國人","createTime":"2019-03-06T16:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T09:37:29.000Z","uid":99700,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"531785717d199632356aec3b5d6d4fce5c9bb5d0","tid":1049962,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T16:08:43.000Z","msg":"一個英國人，一個法國人，一個中國人，一同欣賞一幅伊甸園亞當夏娃的畫。 <br />\n&quot;他們顯然是英國人，&quot;英國人說: &quot;她只有一個蘋果，卻分了給他吃。&quot; <br />\n&quot;不，&quot; 法國人說: &quot;他們一起裸體吃水果，一定是法國人。&quot; <br />\n中國人斬釘截鐵地說: &quot;他們一定是中國人，他們沒衣服穿，差不多沒東西吃，卻依然以為自己在樂園裏。&quot;"},{"pid":"017f79a5d24a370944e7a0a189ffb69b4f77a7a0","tid":1049962,"uid":151354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T16:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9ce51f2216c29b18ddd208bb3bfe574e37b7ec","tid":1049962,"uid":141782,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T16:23:38.000Z","msg":"一定唔係中國人<br />\n係中國人食撚咗條蛇啦"},{"pid":"608811f51f38c0aff13617087780fa9b74c0c3eb","tid":1049962,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa9ce51f2216c29b18ddd208bb3bfe574e37b7ec","tid":1049962,"uid":141782,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T16:23:38.000Z","msg":"一定唔係中國人<br />\n係中國人食撚咗條蛇啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T16:24:26.000Z","msg":"我靜係知佢地一定唔係意大利人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2094b11e45a265f3f12bd705294a4f4d45d0cca7","tid":1049962,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T16:25:34.000Z","msg":"高質"},{"pid":"8722dc79c628dcf974350026fc0b0f8cdfc0a92b","tid":1049962,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa9ce51f2216c29b18ddd208bb3bfe574e37b7ec","tid":1049962,"uid":141782,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T16:23:38.000Z","msg":"一定唔係中國人<br />\n係中國人食撚咗條蛇啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T16:35:59.000Z","ms